snippet.title: Skate Hooligans
snippet.description:
https://gemioli.com/hooligans/

Cowabunga! Little hooligans are on the way! Choose your hero and arrange an amazing disorder ^_^ Collect coins, upgrade bonuses, buy cool skateboards, avoid dangerous obstacles and get scores as much as you can.

Music and sound design by http://volkovstudio.com
